data.description: Welcome home to this beautiful 2 story loctaed on a half size cul-de-sac with mature trees. Close access to everything. Main level hardwood floors with vaulted ceilings in the living room along with a gas fireplace to keep you warm and cozy. Stainless steel appliances/Central air to keep you cool in the summer. Loft could easliy be converted into a 3rd bedroom.
